title: Who's Your Daddy?!

description: This week David Garofalo, Jonathan MrJonathan Barbeau and Chuck Morrison are joined by Jeremy Soares from My Father Cigars and David 'Doc' Diaz as they smoke Jamie Garcia and Davidoff Millennium Cigars. Plus, The Ten Commandments of Cigars, and a special preview of Two Guys 26th Anniversary Party! It’s time for the finer things in life... It’s time for The Cigar Authority!
